un ven m'hot im, er iz gevorn,

00:01:30.256 --> 00:01:32.919
ikh hob fargesn dos vort,

00:01:34.866 --> 00:01:38.707
er, bafrayt fun militer

00:01:35.107 --> 00:01:36.377
bafrayt

00:01:38.865 --> 00:01:42.352
iz hobn mir khasene gehat, un

00:01:42.409 --> 00:01:47.350
azoy hobn mir ongehoybn, er hot keynem nisht gehat, farlorn

00:01:47.350 --> 00:01:50.371
eyn bruder hot er gehat in Pariz

00:01:50.371 --> 00:01:58.958
un eynem vos iz gekumen nor a shtik far der milkhome in Argentine, un azoy di gantse mishpokhe hot er farlorn.

00:01:59.419 --> 00:02:02.231
mir zenen geven eynzam, un

00:02:03.688 --> 00:02:06.540
velkhe arbet hot ir geton mit di kinder?

