00:02:14.016 --> 00:02:18.144
un shepn nakhes vi sheyn zey

00:02:18.150 --> 00:02:22.902
zey flegn oyszen nokhn bod mit di lange hemdlekh

00:02:23.365 --> 00:02:31.504
un ophitn zey, geyn shpatsirn, un, un dos gelt vos ikh fleg fardinen

00:02:31.504 --> 00:02:32.271
fleg ikh k-

