yugntlekhe vos hobn zikh gegreyt tsum forn keyn Yisroel.

00:03:10.767 --> 00:03:19.215
mir hobn gehat, zenen gekumen tsvey shvesters, un gebrengt mit zikh fun Byalistok.

00:03:19.390 --> 00:03:23.788
zey hobn iber- a, a shvester a kalike

00:03:24.317 --> 00:03:28.850
in gantsn a nisht normale

